Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)

How will I receive my subscription?
Once you have made the payment, you can expect to receive an email with your login credentials within 1 to 3 working hours.
Can I use my IPTV subscription on multiple devices?
Yes, you can use your subscription on multiple devices, but not in the same time( not simultaneously.)
Will you renew my subscription automatically?
We will contact you via email to renew your subscription once it is about to expire.
Can I access the IPTV service while traveling?
Yes, our IPTV service is accessible worldwide, you can enjoy your favorite channels and content wherever you are.
Can I request a specific channel or content?
Contact our customer support for requests. We’ll do our best to accommodate, although we cannot guarantee additions of specific channels or content.
Can I request a refund?
You have the option to request a refund within 7 days of subscribing to any paid plan, And we will be more than happy to assist you with your request.
